ams Figma, Zeplin, Adobe CC This role reports to the Sr. Product Designer Manager. Please include your portfolio in addition to resume. Submissions without a portfolio included will not be considered. What We Offer: Competitive salary and 401K. 100% paid health coverage (for you and your family) that includes dental and vision plans. Flexible working hours, including the ability to work from home (on occasion or as needed) Unlimited paid time off Plenty of free food at the office, 4 rotating kegs on tap. Regular team-wide outdoor events and parties. Up to $50/month wellness benefit at a gym or wellness group of your choice Your choice of the latest, top-of-the-line equipment and tools to work with. Work with heaps of smart, awesome people, including a surprising number of people who are great at pool, pinball, and foosball. TRON-BitTorrent is an equal opportunity employer and values diversity at our company. We do not discriminate on the basis of race, religion, color, national origin, gender, sexual orientation, age, marital status, veteran status or disability status. ", 
